2Ethics%20Panel%20To%20Submit%20Report%20On%20Mahua%20Moitra%20In%20Parliament%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20ethics%20committee%20will%20present%20its%20report%20on%20the%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20suggest%20parliament%20to%20expel%20Ms%20Moitra%20from%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20is%20expected%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20division%20of%20votes%20on%20the%20report.%20The%20BJP%20has%2C%20however%2C%20prepared%20for%20this%20and%20issued%20a%20whip%20to%20its%20MPs%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20members%20of%20the%20ethics%20committee%20had%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20report.%20Four%20members%20belonging%20to%20the%20Opposition%20gave%20dissent%20notes.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20called%20the%20report%20a%20%26quot%3Bfixed%20match%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20and%20Opposition%20MPs%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20ethics%20committee%20meeting%20on%20November%202%20after%20questioning%20the%20way%20the%20meeting%20was%20conducted.%20The%20committee%2C%20however%2C%20had%20shot%20back%20saying%20she%20did%20not%20cooperate%20and%20left%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20answering%20more%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20has%20called%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%2C%20who%20filed%20the%20complaint%20with%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20her%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex%26quot%3B.%20Following%20the%20complaint%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20had%20led%20the%20call%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegation%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20gave%20her%20parliament%20login%20ID%20to%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20target%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Ms%20Moitra%20has%20refuted%20the%20cash-for-query%20allegations%2C