%20will%20generate%2030GW%20to%20power%20over%2020%20million%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFMIe8ln7Gn%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FFMIe8ln7Gn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Gautam%20Adani%20(%40gautam_adani)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgautam_adani%2Fstatus%2F1732716869738721700%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20just%20150%20km%20away%2C%20in%20our%20karmabhoomi%20Mundra%2C%20we%20are%20creating%20one%20of%20the%20globe's%20most%20extensive%20and%20integrated%20renewable%20energy%20manufacturing%20ecosystems%20for%20solar%20and%20wind.%20This%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20India's%20journey%20towards%20sustainable%20energy%2C%20underlining%20our%20commitment%20to%20the%20Solar%20Alliance%20and%20the%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%20initiative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20chairman%2C%20along%20with%20the%20X%20post%2C%20shared%20a%20few%20pictures%20where%20the%20ongoing%20large-scale%20project%20could%20be%20seen%20taking%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Adani%20Group%20project%20is%20expected%20to%20add%20to%20India's%20green%20energy%20capacity%2C%20besides%20helping%20in%20reaching%20its%20climate%20action%20pledges%20it%20made%20at%20COP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20committed%20to%20an%20ambitious%20five-part%20%26quot%3BPanchamrit%26quot%3B%20pledge%20at%20COP26%2C%20held%20in%202021.%20They%20included%20reaching%20500%20GW%20of%20non-fossil%20electricity%20capacity%2C%20generating%20half%20of%20all%20energy%20requirements%20from%20renewables%2C%20to%20reducing%20emissions%20by%201%20billion%20tonnes%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20aims%20to%20reduce%20the%20emissions%20intensity%20of%20GDP%20by%2045%20per%20cent.%20Finally%2C%20India%20commits%20to%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202070.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%2