%20Sreesanth%20has%20replied%20with%20his%20own%20view%20in%20the%20post's%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20exceeded%20the%20boundaries%20of%20a%20sportsman%20and%20a%20brother%2C%20and%20above%20all%2C%20you%20represent%20the%20people.%20Yet%2C%20you%20continue%20to%20engage%20in%20conflicts%20with%20every%20cricketer.%20What%20is%20the%20matter%20with%20you%3F%20All%20I%20did%20was%20smile%20and%20observe%2C%20and%20you%20labeled%20me%20a%20fixer%3F%20Seriously%3F%20Are%20you%20above%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3F%20You%20have%20no%20authority%20to%20speak%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20and%20say%20whatever%20you%20please.%20You%20even%20verbally%20abused%20the%20umpires%2C%20and%20yet%20you%20speak%20of%20smiling%3F%20You%20are%20an%20arrogant%20and%20utterly%20classless%20individual%20who%20lacks%20any%20form%20of%20respect%20for%20those%20who%20supported%20you.%20Until%20yesterday%2C%20I%20always%20held%20respect%20for%20you%20and%20your%20family.%20However%2C%20you%20used%20the%20derogatory%20term%20%26quot%3Bfixer%26quot%3B%20not%20just%20once%2C%20but%20seven%20or%20eight%20times.%20You%20even%20resorted%20to%20using%20the%20F-word%20towards%20the%20umpires%20and%20myself%2C%20persistently%20trying%20to%20provoke%20me.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20experienced%20what%20I%20have%20endured%20would%20never%20forgive%20you.%20Deep%20down%2C%20you%20know%20that%20what%20you%20said%20and%20did%20was%20wrong.%20Im%20sure%20even%20God%20wont%20forgive%20you.%20You%20didn't%20even%20come%20to%20the%20field%20aftwr%20that.%20Come%20on%2C%20God%20is%20watching%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20commented%20on%20Gambhir's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0LLC%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20regarding%20the%20argument%20between%20the%20two%20players%20and%20said%20they%20will%20conduct%20an%20internal%20investigation%20on%20the%20violation%20of%20the%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20New