3E%3Cspan%3ELuck%20By%20Chance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20most%20of%20her%20films%20have%20had%20glimpses%20of%20the%20nifty%20touch%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20been%20easy%20to%20spot%20the%20compromises%20she%E2%80%99s%20made%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20film%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%98flop%E2%80%99%20like%20her%20debut.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20obvious%20casting%20of%20Katrina%20Kaif%20sounding%20like%20a%20self-help%20book%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EZindagi%20Na%20Milegi%20Dobara%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2011)%2C%20the%20drawn-out%2C%20insipid%20climax%20of%20the%20otherwise%20observant%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDil%20Dhadakne%20Do%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2015)%2C%20or%20even%20the%20feel-good%2C%20corporate-tested%20journey%20afforded%20to%20a%20Muslim%20hip-hop%20sensation%20from%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20tracks%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fgully-boy-movie-review%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGully%20Boy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2019)%2C%20each%20Akhtar%20film%20has%20felt%20more%20accommodating%20than%20the%20last.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20being%20someone%20who%20trusted%20the%20audience%20to%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20in%20her%20debut%2C%20like%20that%20astoundingly-performed%20first%20scene%20between%20Alyy%20Khan%20and%20Konkona%20Sen%20Sharma%20%E2%80%93%20which%20goes%20from%20parody%20to%20somewhere%20dark%20in%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20%E2%80%93%20Akhtar%2C%20in%20her%20latest%20film%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(based%20on%20the%20famous%20American%20comics%20of%20the%20same%20name)%2C%20has%20included%20a%20song%20called%20%E2%80%98Everything%20is%20Politics%E2%80%99.%20Written%20probably%20to%20wake%20a%20South%20Bombay%20brat%20out%20of%20their%20slumber%20to%20become%20socially%20conscious%2C%20the%20song%20pretty%20much%20distils%20the%20problems%20with%20Akhtar%E2%80%99s%20latest%20film.%20The%20intentions%20are%20pure%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20idealism%20permeating%20through%20it%2C%20but%20the%20song%20(like%20the%20film)%20takes%20place%20in%20such%20a%20cocoon%20of%20privilege%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20take%20seriously%20beyond%20a%20point.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F07zwmOypaV8%3Fsi%3DaxXzxfueezlIGcMK%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhtar%E2%80%99s%20adaptation%20is%20set%20in%20a%20fictitious%20British-Indian%20hill%20station%20(presumably%20in%20Northern%20India)%20called%20Riverdale%2C%20in%201964.%20Just%20like%20the%20comics%2C%20the%20tone%20of%20the%20film%20feels%20Utopian%2C%20where%20everyone%20acts%20in%20good%20faith%2C%20including%20the%20antagonist.%20The%20performances%20seem%20deliberately%20high-pitched%2C%20drawing%20attention%20to%20their%20theatricality.%20Most%20characters%20embody%20one-note%20tropes%2C%20which%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20for%20writing%20about%20groups%20(like%20the%20sitcom%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFriends%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20to%20love%20triangles%20(like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKuch%20Kuch%20Hota%20Hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E17-year-old%20Archie%20Andrews%20(Agastya%20Nanda)%2C%20apart%20from%20being%20in%20high%20school%2C%20works%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20travel%20agency%20and%20is%20the%20lead%20singer%20for%20his%20band%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Betty%20Cooper%20(Khushi%20Kapoor)%20is%20the%20girl%20next%20door%20who%20is%20overly%20caring%20and%20generous%20to%20people%20around%20her.%20Veronica%20Lodge%20(Suhana%20Khan)%20is%20Riverdale%E2%80%99s%20vivacious%20prom%20queen%2C%20daughter%20of%20the%20industrialist%20Mr%20Lodge%20(Alyy%20Khan)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20man%20behind%20the%20plan%20to%20tear%20down%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20centrally%20located%20park%20to%20build%20a%20hotel.%20The%20screenplay%20(written%20by%20Ayesha%20Devitre%20Dhillon%2C%20Reema%20Kagti%20and%20Akhtar)%20introduces%20obstacles%20in%20every%20other%20scene%2C%20only%20to%20resolve%20them%20swiftly.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20death%20knell%20for%20any%20film%2C%20when%20the%20%E2%80%98rules%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20world%20suggest%20that%20anything%20goes%2C%20or%20nothing%20matters.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20what%20anyone%20does%20after%20this%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20headed%20towards%20the%20rainbow%20of%20%E2%80%98happily%20ever%20after%E2%80%99%20soon%20enough.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuzanne%20Caplan%20Merwanji%E2%80%99s%20immaculate%20production%20design%20and%20Dhara%20Jain%E2%80%99s%20precise%20set%20decoration%20reminded%20me%20of%20Greta%20Gerwig%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarbie%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20deliberate%20falseness%20to%20the%20surroundings%2C%20to%20make%20it%20look%20like%20we%E2%80%99re%20inside%20a%20comic%20strip.%20However%2C%20while%20Gerwig%20used%20the%20world%20of%20the%20film%20to%20ask%20more%20pressing%20questions%20of%20it%2C%20Akhtar%20is%20relatively%20less%20successful.%20There%20are%20flourishes%20of%20%E2%80%98revisionism%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Veronica%20and%20Betty%20confront%20Archie%20about%20his%20%E2%80%98confusion%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20how%20Reggie%20(Vedang%20Raina)%2C%20the%20jock%20of%20the%20group%2C%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20the%20most%20sensitive.%20There%20are%20real-world%20allusions%20to%20the%20free%20press%2C%20the%20independence%20struggle%20in%201947%2C%20and%20capitalism%20trumping%20all-round%20development%2C%20but%20they%20all%20feel%20mostly%20incidental%20by%20the%20end.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20overwhelming%20naivete%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20drilled%20into%20most%20of%20the%20characters%2C%20including%20the%20elders%20in%20the%20town.%20When%20bookseller%20Hal%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20(Satyajit%20Sharma)%20shop%20is%20overrun%20so%20that%20the%20town%20can%20have%20its%20plaza%20%E2%80%93%20he%E2%80%99s%20tensed%20about%20it%20in%20one%20moment%2C%20and%20joyous%20about%20landing%20a%20job%20as%20an%20assistant%20manager%20at%20the%20store%20of%20his%20corporate%20rival%20in%20the%20next.%20Later%2C%20he%20refuses%20to%20sign%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20razing%20down%20of%20the%20park%20for%20Mr%20Lodge%E2%80%99s%20hotel%20%E2%80%93%20because%20he%20considers%20it%20would%20not%20be%20gracious%20on%20his%20part.%20I%20realise%20what%20Akhtar%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20here%2C%20but%20it%20works%20more%20in%20theory.%20In%20a%20different%20scene%20between%20Veronica%20and%20Mr%20Lodge%20%E2%80%93%20he%20questions%20her%20about%20her%20convenient%20activism%20to%20not%20lose%20face%20in%20front%20of%20friends%2C%20even%20though%20she%E2%80%99s%20never%20had%20a%20question%20about%20how%20her%20father%20earns%20the%20riches%20she%E2%80%99s%20happy%20to%20splurge%20otherwise.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20fine%20moment%20that%20could%E2%80%99ve%20prompted%20introspection%20in%20Veronica%2C%20which%20could%E2%80%99ve%20also%20doubled%20up%20as%20a%20meta-commentary%20on%20Suhana%20Khan%20being%20forced%20to%20introspect%20about%20being%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20film%20star%20in%20the%20world.%20Alas%2C%20the%20moment%20is%20left%20hanging%20in%20the%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%20cast%2C%20only%20Vedang%20Raina%20and%20Aditi%20Saigal%20(Dot)%20seem%20to%20exhibit%20sparks%20of%20spontaneity.%20Khushi%20Kapoor%20as%20Betty%20is%20adorable%20as%20someone%20who%20spends%20a%20large%20part%20of%20her%20screen%20time%20looking%20longingly%20at%20Archie%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20about%20it.%20Mihir%20Ahuja%20plays%20%E2%80%98Jughead%E2%80%99%20Jones%20with%20an%20exaggerated%20awkwardness%2C%20as%20the%20ever-hungry%20chap%2C%20with%20a%20firm%20grip%20on%20right%20and%20wrong.%20Nanda%20and%20Khan%2C%20both%2C%20seem%20too%20aware%20of%20the%20camera%20to%20treat%20their%20performances%20as%20anything%20other%20than%20an%20extension%20of%20their%20real-life%20personas%20around%20mobile%20phones%20or%20the%20paparazzi.%20Everything%20is%20too%20groomed%2C%20and%20every%20word%20(dialogues%20by%20Farhan%20Akhtar)%20coming%20out%20of%20their%20mouth%20feels%20air-brushed.%20These%20young%20actors%20are%20earnest%2C%20but%20they%20also%20seem%20too%20boot-camped%2C%20though%20it%20might%20not%20be%20fair%20to%20fully%20judge%20their%20acting%20potential%20on%20this%20one%20film%20alone.%20Among%20the%20supporting%20cast%2C%20Puja%20Sarup%20%E2%80%93%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Riverdale%20council%2C%20who%20pilfers%20the%20biscuits%20in%20a%20tissue%20at%20the%20end%20of%20every%20council%20meeting%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20only%20one%20who%20makes%20an%20impression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20surely%20not%20Zoya%20Akhtar%E2%80%99s%20finest%20hour.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20mollycoddled%20ode%20to%20a%20bygone%20era%2C%20a%20frothy%20concoction%20pandering%20to%20its%20audience.%20The%20world-building%2C%20the%20songs%20and%20the%20set-pieces%20are%20nicely%20done%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20make%20this%20143-minute%20film%20feel%20any%20tighter%20and%20shorter.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20sign%20of%20our%20times%20that%20something%20even%20slightly%20topical%20or%20rebellious%20needs%20to%20be%20buried%20so%20deep%20into%20a%20world%2C%20surrounded%20by%20distractions%20that%20it%20makes%20the%20commentary%20almost%20ineffective.%20As%20any%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELuck%20By%20Chance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20fan%20would%20attest%20to%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20the%20most%20pliant%20Akhtar%20has%20ever%20been.%20So%2C%20looking%20at%20the%20bright%20side%2C%20the%20only%20way%20from%20here%20is%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701959361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07191933%2FScreenshot-2023-12-07-at-7.18.42%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fthe-archies-zoya-akhtar-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world-building%2C%20the%20songs%20and%20the%20set-pieces%20are%20nicely%20done%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20make%20this%20143-minute%20film%20feel%20any%20tighter%20and%20shorter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fthe-archies-zoya-akhtar-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Who%20Shot%20Dead%203%20At%20US%20University%20Was%20Denied%20Job%20As%20Professor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20who%20opened%20fire%20at%20Las%20Vegas%20University%20killing%20three%20people%20and%20injuring%20one%20more%20was%20a%2067-year-old%20professor%20who%20was%20denied%20a%20job%20at%20the%20university%2C%20reports%20said%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20professor%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20named%20yet%2C%20was%20later%20shot%20dead%20by%20the%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20our%20investigators%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20we%20have%20three%20dead%20victims%20and%20one%20additional%20victim%20in%20critical%20condition%20at%20a%20local%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Metropolitan%20Police%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bactive%20shooter%26quot%3B%20was%20also%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20police%20say%20they%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20idea%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20clear%20motive%20behind%20the%20shooting%2C%20the%20man%20is%20said%20to%20have%20previously%20worked%20at%20universities%20in%20Georgia%20and%20North%20Carolina%20before%20applying%20at%20the%20Vegas%20institute%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Las%20Vegas%20police%20said%20they%20received%20information%20about%20shots%20being%20fired%20at%20two%20locations%20inside%20the%20university%20campus%20around%20noon%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20which%20officers%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20soon%20engaged%20in%20a%20gunbattle%20with%20the%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20few%20hours%2C%20the%20university%20continued%20to%20urge%20students%20and%20those%20in%20campus%20to%20shelter%20in%20place%20in%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BUniversity%20Police%20responding%20to%20confirmed%20active%20shooter%20in%20BEH.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20test.%20RUN-HIDE-FIGHT%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20posts%20read%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20common%20response%20tactic%20to%20mass%20shootings%2C%20a%20common%20phenomenon%20in%20the%20US.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20country%20has%20recorded%20over%20630%20such%20shooting%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Las%20Vegas%20witnessed%20one%20of%20America's%20deadliest-ever%20mass%20shootings%2C%20when%20a%20gunman%20opened%20fire%20on%20a%20crowded%20music%20festival%2C%20killing%2060%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701959220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fle7jsdco_university-of-nevada-las-vegas_625x300_07_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-who-shot-dead-3-at-us-university-was-denied-job-as-professor-4643363%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20who%20opened%20fire%20at%20Las%20Vegas%20University%20killing%20three%20people%20and%20injuring%20one%20more%20was%20a%2067-year-old%20professor%20who%20was%20denied%20a%20job%20at%20the%20university%2C%20reports%20said