ills.%20However%2C%20authorities%20foiled%20the%20march%20and%20restrictions%20similar%20to%20the%20day%20when%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down%20were%20imposed%20in%20Rajouri.%20This%20is%20undemocratic%2C%20but%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20our%20voice%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zahid%20Parwaz%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20Gujjar%20leader%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Gujjar%20Bakarwal%20Youth%20Welfare%20Conference%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(Rajouri)%20S.P.N.%20Amritpal%20Singh%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20despite%20repeated%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20that%20security%20personnel%20set%20up%20checkpoints%20and%20blockades%20on%20roads%20in%20Thanamandi%20and%20adjoining%20areas%20of%20Rajouri%20district%20on%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20where%20passenger%20and%20private%20vehicles%20were%20frisked%20and%20all%20those%20who%20were%20planning%20to%20join%20the%20march%20against%20the%20Bills%20were%20deboarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98The%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98The%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%E2%80%99%20were%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session%20in%20July%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20notification%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20said%20that%20the%20two%20Bills%2C%20which%20will%20also%20extend%20political%20reservation%20to%20the%20Paharis%2C%20are%20listed%20under%20%E2%80%98Legislative%20Business%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1981907%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Clikely%20to%20be%20taken%20up%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20ongoing%20session%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Parliament%20Passed%20Two%20Important%20Laws%20on%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Here's%20What%20They%20Will%20Do.%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-passed-two-important-laws-on-jk-heres-what-they-will-do%5C%22%3EParliament%20Passed%20Two%20Important%20Laws%20on%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20They%20Will%20Do.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuftar%20Ahmad%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20Gujjar%20activist%2C%20said%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20communities%20were%20feeling%20betrayed%20by%20the%20listing%20of%20the%20two%20Bills%20and%20the%20crackdown%20on%20protesters%20was%20%E2%80%9Cadding%20salt%20to%20our%20wounds%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20democratic%20country.%20Peaceful%20protest%20is%20our%20constitutional%20right%20but%20unfortunately%20it%20is%20not%20being%20allowed.%20The%20government%20has%20been%20telling%20the%20world%20that%20the%20tribals%20benefited%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20but%20why%20are%20people%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20the%20roads%20then%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Bills%20came%20despite%20assurances%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greaterkashmir.com%2Fjammu%2Freservation-for-pahari-community-wont-affect-gujjars-bakerwals-lg-manoj-sinha%2F%5C%22%3Elieutenant%20governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20reservation%20percentages%20for%20the%20Gujjar%20and%20Bakkerwal%20tribes%20will%20not%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20new%20chunk%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20population%20to%20the%20ST%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Paharis%2C%20the%20Bills%20will%20provide%20reservation%20in%20jobs%2C%20educational%20institutions%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20legislature%20under%20the%20ST%20category%20(10%25%20in%20J%26amp%3BK)%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Gadda%20Brahmin%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Koli%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Paddari%20Tribe%E2%80%99%20communities%2C%20thereby%20shrinking%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20already-defined%20ST%20communities%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeeling%20dismayed%2C%20the%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20parts%20of%20Jammu%20as%20well%20as%20on%20social%20media%20to%20vent%20their%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESporadic%20protests%20also%20broke%20out%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20Jammu%20division%20against%20the%20Bills.%20At%20the%20University%20of%20Jammu%2C%20a%20protest%20was%20held%20on%20Wednesday%20(December%206)%20by%20tribal%20students%2C%20prompting%20the%20police%20to%20enter%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20protest%20verified%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20policemen%20in%20riot%20gear%20striding%20around%20the%20university%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPolice%20entered%20in%20Jammu%20University%20campus%20and%20started%20arresting%20Gujjar%20Bakerwal%20students%20as%20they%20were%20doing%20Protest%20against%20the%20Bills%20in%20which%20all%20elite%20classes%20being%20added%20into%20ST%20Status.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FABVbv7Er2w%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FABVbv7Er2w%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Zahid%20Parwaz%20Choudhary%20(%40ZahidParwaz)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZahidParwaz%2Fstatus%2F1732372618018472306%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20shot%20on%20Wednesday%20showed%20the%20protesting%20students%20shouting%20anti-police%20slogans%20and%20taking%20out%20a%20candlelight%20march%20while%20alleging%20that%20they%20were%20assaulted%20by%20cops%20%E2%80%9Cmerely%20for%20exercising%20their%20democratic%20rights%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHalla%20in%20Jammu%20University%20Gujjar%20students%20protesting%20against%20unconstitutional%20Bill%20which%20has%20been%20enlisted%20in%20this%20Parliament%20session.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPSYKtZHPef%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPSYKtZHPef%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Zahid%20Parwaz%20Choudhary%20(%40ZahidParwaz)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZahidParwaz%2Fstatus%2F1732375137713098843%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20protest%20was%20also%20planned%20by%20Gujjar%20and%20Bakkerwal%20groups%20in%20Srinagar%20city%20on%20Thursday%20against%20the%20two%20Bills.%20However%2C%20authorities%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20some%20activists%20from%20the%20tribal%20communities%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20the%20Lal%20Chowk%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20centre%2C%20during%20which%20they%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20withdraw%20the%20two%20Bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20130%20activists%20and%20several%20students%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20are%20set%20to%20appear%20in%20exams%2C%20have%20been%20detained.%20We%20urge%20the%20authorities%20to%20reconsider%20the%20Bills%20and%20release%20all%20the%20detainees%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20activist%20who%20addressed%20the%20presser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20not%20be%20immediately%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20defended%20the%20Bills%20in%20parliament%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20will%20add%20%E2%80%9Canother%20pearl%20to%20the%20chain%20of%20hundreds%20of%20progressive%20changes%E2%80%9D%20brought%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20Bills%20are%20going%20to%20provide%20rights%20and%20justice%20to%20those%20who%20were%20treated%20unjustly%20and%20insulted%20and%20ignored%20for%2070%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%202011%20census%2C%20there%20are%20between%20eight%20and%2012%20lakh%20Pahari-speaking%20people%2C%20and%20about%2015%20lakh%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20live%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20which%20comprises%20the%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20districts%20of%20Jammu%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20can%20collectively%20impact%20the%20outcome%20of%20elections%20in%2025%20out%20of%2090%20seats%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20assembly%2C%20according%20to%20one%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20wooing%20the%20Paharis%20to%20make%20inroads%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20where%20it%20hopes%20to%20dent%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20traditional%20parties%20like%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party.%20Critics%20allege%20the%20party%20is%20attempting%20to%20create%20divisions%20between%20the%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20the%20Paharis%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fa-culture-of-indifference-what-the-bakarwals-of-jammu-and-kashmir-endure%5C%22%3EA%20Culture%20of%20Indifference%3A%20What%20the%20Bakarwals%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Endure%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujjar-Bakkerwal%20tribes%20and%20the%20Pahari%20community%20share%20a%20similar%20social%20and%20cultural%20milieu%2C%20and%20together%20they%20form%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20mostly%20live%20a%20nomadic%20life%20by%20shuttling%20between%20the%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20regions%20with%20their%20livestock%20of%20buffaloes%2C%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20the%20Paharis%20are%20a%20socially%20stratified%20community%20with%20caste%20and%20other%20ethnic%20divisions%20who%20are%20joined%20by%20the%20thread%20of%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20passed%2C%20the%20Bills%20will%20be%20the%20first%20of%20their%20kind%20to%20not%20only%20grant%20tribal%20status%20to%20a%20linguistic%20group%2C%20but%20also%20provide%20them%20with%20political%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20two%20Bills%20on%20ST%20status%20for%20Paharis%2C%20three%20more%20Bills%20on%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20will%20restructure%20the%20reservation%20rules%20and%20representation%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20during%20the%20ongoing%20parliament%20session%20which%20started%20on%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribal%20groups%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20since%20December%2025%2C%202019%2C%20when%20a%20delegation%20of%20Paharis%20met%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20sought%20ST%20status%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20the%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20have%20been%20organising%20events%2C%20candlelight%20marches%2C%20protests%20and%20even%20a%20couple%20of%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3Es%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20express%20their%20anger%20against%20the%20likely%20grant%20of%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202020%2C%20the%20Paharis%20were%20given%20a%204%25%20reservation%20in%20the%20OBC%20category.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Commission%20on%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Classes%20headed%20by%20G.D.%20Sharma%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202022%20report%2C%20the%20commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greaterkashmir.com%2Fkashmir%2Fpaddaris-kolis-and-gadda-brahmans-of-jk-to-get-st-status-along-with-paharis%2F%5C%22%3Erecommended%20the%20inclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Paharis%2C%20Paddari%2C%20Koli%20and%20Gadda%20Brahmin%20communities%20as%20Scheduled%20Tribes.