%9D%20The%20tribal%20leader%20also%20added%20that%20the%20state%20has%20all%20the%20facilities%20and%20if%20they%20have%20the%20intention%20to%20return%20the%20bodies%2C%20then%20they%20should%20have%20returned%20them%20by%20helicopter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20leader%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%20(KSO)%2C%20in%20a%20telephonic%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Freport-in-sc-on-manipur-victims-bodies-in-morgues-highlights-deep-divides-state-of-law-and-order%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ealso%20questioned%20the%20Manipur%20government%20on%20not%20letting%20tribal%20Leaders%20enter%20Imphal%20to%20verify%20and%20claim%20the%20bodies%20lying%20in%20the%20capital%E2%80%99s%20hospitals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECompensation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20compensation%20plan%20announced%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20in%20June%2C%20the%20committee%20stated%20in%20court%20that%20there%20were%20a%20few%20families%20who%20had%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20compensation%20offered%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20dead%20to%20accept%20money%20at%20this%20stage%20from%20the%20very%20state%20that%20engineered%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing.%20Hence%20the%20overall%20feeling%20is%20that%20after%20the%20dead%20bodies%20are%20buried%20with%20dignity%20according%20to%20tribal%20customs%2C%20then%20a%20decision%20can%20and%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20regarding%20compensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20tribal%20organisations%20said%20in%20response.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EReconstruction%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kuki%20community%20also%20questioned%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20on%20not%20initiating%20the%20construction%20of%20tribal%20houses%20and%20churches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20said%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20comprehend%20how%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20could%20have%20said%20in%20court%20that%20the%20state%20was%20fully%20cooperating%20in%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20the%20displaced%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20been%20apprised%20that%20more%20than%207%2C750%20tribal%20houses%20in%20197%20villages%20were%20destroyed%20in%20the%20violence%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months.%20The%20work%20to%20rebuild%20them%20has%20not%20begun.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20without%20discussing%20with%20the%20tribal%20organisations%2C%20a%20contractor%20from%20Delhi%20has%20begun%20setting%20up%20plastic%20Porta%20cabins%20in%20some%20places.%20These%20cabins%20are%20unsuitable%20for%20the%20climate%20conditions%20in%20the%20hills%20where%20heavy%20winds%2C%20rain%20and%20landslides%20are%20common.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20top%20court%20was%20told%20about%20the%20359%20churches%20that%20were%20destroyed.%20However%2C%20construction%20work%20to%20rebuild%20them%20has%20not%20started.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701946851000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05160550%2FDhL0M9tUYAEIhu0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-sc-committee-kuki-groups-dialogue-deny-report-findings%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20groups%20said%20the%20committee%20only%20met%20with%20a%20few%20tribal%20leaders%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20but%20ignored%20the%20leading%20civil%20society%20organisations%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-sc-committee-kuki-groups-dialogue-deny-report-findings%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20banks%20ask%20fintech%20partners%20to%20limit%20tiny%20persona