e%20in%20Brooklyn%20and%20have%20grown%20to%20call%20it%20a%20home.%20I%20now%20make%20makloubeh%20with%20lal%20mirch%20and%20garam%20masala.%20Pita%20bread%20with%20zaatar%20and%20olive%20oil%20has%20become%20my%20go-to%20midnight%20snack.%20I%20have%20gotten%20drunk%20on%20arak%20and%20unsuccessfully%20danced%20dabke%20at%20parties.%20The%20Delhi%20boy%20in%20me%20has%20also%20learned%20to%20cuss%20in%20Arabic%20now.%20These%20friendships%20have%20made%20me%20realise%20how%20similar%20we%20are%20to%20each%20other%20as%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20best%20friend%20in%20the%20city%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20Palestinian%20Christian%20whose%20family%20was%20displaced%20from%20Jerusalem%20in%201948%20and%20has%20lived%20in%20exile%20ever%20since.%20My%20roommate%20is%20from%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20she%20and%20her%20family%20have%20to%20face%20the%20everyday%20humiliation%20of%20crossing%20Israeli%20checkpoints%20to%20travel%20in%20their%20own%20country.%20It%20did%20not%20start%20on%20October%207%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20been%20hearing%20stories%20about%20the%20Israeli%20settler%20violence%20in%20occupied%20Palestine%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20I%20know%20people%20in%20this%20city%20whose%20houses%20have%20been%20bombed%2C%20and%20whose%20family%20members%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20arbitrarily%20arrested%2C%20and%20displaced%20in%20Palestine.%20I%20attach%20human%20faces%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Ramallah%2C%20Nablus%2C%20Bethlehem%20and%20Jerusalem.%20I%20will%20not%20pretend%20to%20write%20from%20a%20neutral%20and%20distanced%20position%20today.%20Neutrality%20often%20helps%20the%20oppressor%2C%20not%20the%20oppressed.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Palestine%20has%20become%20as%20far%20and%20as%20close%20as%20India%2C%20in%20some%20ways.%20When%20I%20read%20the%20news%20from%20Gaza%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20it%20hits%20me%20as%20if%20something%20horrible%20is%20unfolding%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20destruction%20of%20Gaza%20has%20shaken%20the%20world%20to%20the%20core.%20More%20than%2015%2C000%20people%2C%20including%2010%2C000%20women%20and%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza.%20Another%2017%2C00%2C000%20people%20stand%20displaced.%20Numbers%20would%20have%20increased%20by%20the%20time%20you%20read%20this.%20Hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20universities%2C%20homes%2C%20refugee%20shelters%20and%20UN%20offices%20have%20been%20relentlessly%20bombed.%20A%20senior%20UN%20human%20rights%20expert%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F31%2Fun-official-resigns-israel-hamas-war-palestine-new-york%5C%22%3Ecalled%20Gaza%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20genocide%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter.%20Along%20with%20Gaza%2C%20all%20the%20rules%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20have%20been%20bombed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20forces.%20Amidst%20this%20destruction%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20for%20liberation%20has%20found%20renewed%20support%20across%20the%20globe.%20Millions%20have%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Berlin%2C%20Paris%2C%20Cairo%2C%20Amman%2C%20Stockholm%2C%20Amsterdam%2C%20Seoul%2C%20Johannesburg%2C%20Wellington%2C%20Sydney%2C%20Islamabad%2C%20Dhaka%2C%20Sao%20Paulo%2C%20Bogota%2C%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20Santiago%20and%20countless%20other%20cities%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20free%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Israel's%20Goal%20of%20Eliminating%20Hamas%20is%20a%20Red%20Herring%2C%20Evicting%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20is%20the%20Real%20Aim%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-hamas-red-herring-evicting-palestinians-gaza%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20Goal%20of%20Eliminating%20Hamas%20is%20a%20Red%20Herring%2C%20Evicting%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20is%20the%20Real%20Aim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20New%20York%20has%20witnessed%20protests%20every%20single%20day%20for%20the%20past%20two%20months.%20New%20Yorkers%20of%20all%20colours%2C%20classes%2C%20nationalities%2C%20ethnicities%20and%20religious%20backgrounds%20have%20gathered%20on%20the%20streets.%20The%20heart%20of%20the%20American%20empire%20reverberates%20with%20passionate%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9D%20Ceasefire%20now%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free%E2%80%9D%20every%20single%20day.%20Subway%20stations%20are%20sprayed%20with%20graffiti%20in%20support%20of%20Gaza.%20People%20wearing%20keffiyeh%20and%20Palestinian%20flags%20in%20solidarity%20have%20become%20a%20common%20sight.%20Poets%2C%20singers%2C%20writers%2C%20actors%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20musicians%2C%20painters%20and%20academics%20are%20all%20lending%20their%20voices%20to%20the%20cause.%20People%20wave%20Palestinian%20flags%20from%20their%20windows%20and%20bus%20drivers%20honk%20loudly%20in%20solidarity%20as%20protesters%20march%20on%20the%20streets.%20Halal%20carts%2C%20run%20mostly%20by%20Arab%20migrants%2C%20are%20witnessing%20longer%20lines%20for%20chicken%20over%20rice%20orders.%20Volunteer-run%20organisations%20from%20different%20walks%20of%20life%20like%20Jewish%20Voices%20for%20Peace%2C%20Palestinian%20Youth%20Movement%2C%20Within%20Our%20Lifetime%2C%20Answer%20Coalition%2C%20Shut%20it%20Down%20and%20many%20others%20have%20worked%20hard%20to%20organise%20these%20actions.%20American%20Jews%20have%20participated%20in%20heroic%20civil%20disobedience%20actions%2C%20courting%20arrest%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine.%20Students%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20New%20York%20University%20and%20City%20University%20New%20York%2C%20three%20major%20schools%20in%20the%20city%2C%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20calls%20of%20their%20conscience%20by%20demanding%20that%20their%20university%20leadership%20divest%20from%20Israel.%20Walkouts%2C%20teach-ins%2C%20banner%20drops%20and%20cultural%20gatherings%20have%20been%20organised%20on%20campuses%20to%20break%20the%20uncomfortable%20silences.%20This%20is%20our%20generation%E2%80%99s%20Vietnam%20is%20the%20sentiment%20that%20runs%20across%20the%20American%20student%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123836%2FA7xdsZ0CMAAHgmj.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123836%2FA7xdsZ0CMAAHgmj.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123836%2FA7xdsZ0CMAAHgmj-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStudents%20protesting%20at%20NYU.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40Meera_Shakhbout%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversity%20administrations%2C%20under%20pressure%20from%20trustees%20and%20donors%2C%20have%20responded%20with%20vengeance.%20Pro-Palestine%20student%20organisations%20on%20campuses%20have%20been%20suspended%2C%20students%20disciplined%20and%20employees%20terminated.%20Palestine%20has%20become%20the%20limit%20case%20for%20free%20speech%20on%20elite%20US%20university%20campuses.%20All%20liberal%20fa%C3%A7ades%20of%20top%20research%20institutions%20have%20crumbled.%20Universities%20are%20openly%20functioning%20as%20academic%20wings%20of%20the%20American%20military-industrial%20complex.%20These%20gatherings%20in%20New%20York%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Joe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20stood%20in%20support%20of%20the%20belligerent%20Israeli%20occupation.%20They%20have%20supplied%20weapons%2C%20money%20and%20diplomatic%20consent%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20contradictions%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20democracy%20are%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20news%20from%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%20has%20been%20disappointing%20and%20sad.%20The%20Indian%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-palestine-protests-police-crackdown%5C%22%3Ehas%20not%20allowed%20any%20large-scale%20mobilisation%20for%20Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20streets.%20Protesters%20have%20been%20detained%2C%20cultural%20gatherings%20stand%20cancelled%20and%20dissenting%20voices%20have%20been%20stifled.%20A%20certain%20fear%20grips%20the%20argumentative%20Indian%20mind%20on%20the%20question%20of%20Palestine.%20India%2C%20whose%20independence%20from%20the%20British%20empire%20had%20set%20the%20path%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20the%20entire%20colonised%20world%2C%20has%20silently%20witnessed%20a%20genocide%20of%20an%20occupied%20and%20colonised%20people.%20India%2C%20a%20country%20that%20gloriously%20fought%20the%20mightiest%20of%20the%20colonial%20empire%2C%20has%20shown%20reticence%20to%20support%20the%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20Once%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20a%20newly%20independent%20India%2C%20still%20trying%20to%20stand%20on%20its%20feet%2C%20had%20brought%20the%20agenda%20of%20apartheid%20to%20the%20UN%20tables%20to%20speak%20against%20the%20racial%20violence%20of%20the%20colonisers%20and%20became%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20impose%20sanctions%20on%20apartheid%20South%20Africa.%20A%2075-year-old%20India%2C%20set%20to%20become%20a%20global%20superpower%2C%20has%20not%20found%20the%20moral%20courage%20to%20utter%20a%20single%20word%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20apartheid%20regime%2C%20even%20at%20a%20time%20when%20fellow%20countries%20in%20South%20America%20and%20Africa%20have%20severed%20their%20diplomatic%20relationships%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Israel%20Ramps%20up%20Military%20Action%2C%20Protective%20Presence%20Activism%20in%20Palestine%20Is%20No%20Longer%20Working%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-israel-ramps-up-military-action-protective-presence-activism-in-palestine-is-no-longer-working%5C%22%3EAs%20Israel%20Ramps%20up%20Military%20Action%2C%20Protective%20Presence%20Activism%20in%20Palestine%20Is%20No%20Longer%20Working%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20social%20media%20users%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boomlive.in%2Fnews%2Fisrael-palestine-gaza-hamas-middle-east-war-conflict-fake-news-disinfo-meghupdates-ajaychauhan41-mrsinha-jix5a-twitter-x-23311%5C%22%3Econtributed%20most%20to%20the%20online%20disinformation%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Israel-Palestine%2C%20demonising%20Palestinians%20as%20terrorists%20and%20sub-humans%2C%20who%20deserve%20to%20be%20annihilated%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth.%20Mainstream%20Indian%20media%2C%20rotten%20for%20many%20years%20now%2C%20has%20acted%20as%20gaslighter%20par%20excellence.%20Comparing%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20situation%20with%20India-Pakistan%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20intellectual%20error%2C%20when%20in%20reality%20it%20is%20the%20pre-independence%20India-British%20empire%20analogy%20at%20play%20here.%20Israel%20is%20a%20settler%20colonial%20formation%20on%20Palestinian%20lands.%20Would%20we%20Indians%20have%20acknowledged%20the%20British%20colonial%20state%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20exist%20over%20India%3F%20If%20the%20answer%20is%20no%2C%20then%20what%20makes%20us%20ally%20with%20Israel%20today%3F%20The%20relentless%20cheering%20and%20valorisation%20of%20Israeli%20military%20actions%20by%20Noida%20media%20in%20the%20name%20of%20war%20reporting%20has%20only%20contributed%20to%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20global%20consent%20of%20this%20genocide.%20Imagine%20someone%20cheering%20General%20Dyer%20during%20the%20Jallianwala%20Bagh%20massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERabid%20islamophobia%20has%20blinded%20our%20moral%20vision.%20Strategic%20deep%20state%20and%20defence%20partnerships%20with%20Israel%20have%20silenced%20our%20fearless%20political%20voices.%20We%20speak%20in%20measured%20tones%2C%20walking%20tight%20diplomatic%20ropes%20on%20this%20issue.%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3Eabstention%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20resolution%20speaks%20so%20much%20about%20us%20as%20a%20country.%20In%20strategically%20supporting%20Israel%2C%20we%20have%20ended%20up%20supporting%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20war%20crimes%20known%20to%20man.%20Our%20silence%20on%20Palestine%20has%20muted%20all%20the%20values%20of%20our%20freedom%20struggle%20as%20well.%20We%20have%20forgotten%20the%20role%20that%20an%20independent%20post-colonial%20India%20had%20to%20play%20at%20the%20world%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20becoming%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Third%20World%2C%20we%20have%20sadly%20reduced%20ourselves%20to%20the%20status%20of%20a%20strategic%20partner%20of%20a%20morally%20bankrupt%20American%20war%20machinery.%20The%20question%20of%20Palestine%20is%20the%20most%20urgent%20political%20and%20moral%20question%20of%20our%20times.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20a%20question%20for%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%2C%20it%20is%20a%20question%20for%20all%20of%20us%20bearing%20witness.%20It%20stands%20before%20us%20as%20a%20mirror%20demanding%20us%20to%20look%20at%20ourselves%20and%20see%20what%20we%20are%20becoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShikhar%20Goel%20is%20a%20doctoral%20student%20at%20New%20York%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701936037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwitnessing-palestine-in-new-york-and-watching-indias-moral-vision-disappear%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2075-year-old%20India%2C%20set%20to%20become%20a%20global%20superpower%2C%20has%20not%20found%20the%20moral%20courage%20to%20utter%20a%20single%20word%20against%20Israel's%20apartheid%20regime%2C%20even%20at%20a%20time%20when%20fellow%20countries%20in%20South%20America%20and%20Africa%20have%20severed%20their%20diplomatic%20relationships%20with%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwitnessing-palestine-in-new-york-and-watching-indias-moral-vision-disappear%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Excerpt%3A%20Why%20India's%20Social%20Development%20Indicators%20Lag%20Behind%20its%20Neighbours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07112307%2Ffd42a93e-1b05-4602-adbc-827125ca5f01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EUNEQUAL%3A%20Why%20India%20Lags%20Behind%20Its%20Neighbours%20%3Cem%3Eby%20writer%20and%20activist%20Swati%20Narayan%2C%20published%20by%20Westland%20on%20November%2027%2C%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20centre%20was%20a%20joke.%20The%20only%20living%20beings%20on%20the%20premises%20were%20grazing%20in%20the%20courtyard.%20%E2%80%98The%20sacred%20cows%20are%20the%20doctors%2C%E2%80%99%20laughed%20my%20research%20coordinator%2C%20Ismael.%20The%20entire%20building%20was%20dilapidated%E2%80%94floors%20broken%2C%20walls%20collapsing%2C%20paint%20peeling%20and%20weeds%20growing%20in%20the%20rooms%20and%20roof.%20In%20the%20village%20we%20were%20visiting%2C%20this%20was%20the%20only%20health%20centre%20within%20a%20kilometre%20radius.%20The%20doctors%20and%20health%20workers%20had%20obviously%20abandoned%20this%20workplace%20despite%20continuing%20to%20draw%20a%20hefty%20government%20salary.%20The%20only%20other%20health%20facility%20was%20more%20than%2014%20kilometres%20away.%20Bihar%20does%20have%20better%20health%20centres.%20But%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Kishanganj%20district%2C%20most%20government%20services%20we%20saw%20were%20similarly%20in%20shambles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20also%20went%20to%20the%20homes%20of%20two%20accredited%20social%20health%20activists%20(ASHAs)%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20village%20as%20doorstep%20health%20workers.%20Neither%20of%20them%20had%20received%20any%20medicines%20for%20two%20years%20and%20we%20heard%20a%20litany%20of%20complaints.%20Their%20kits%20only%20had%20old%20oral%20rehydration%20salt%20(ORS)%20packets%20and%20a%20few%20government%20brands%20of%20condoms%20and%20contraceptive%20pills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20323px)%2085vw%2C%20323px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22323%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2.jpg%20793w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2-198x300.jpg%20198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2-677x1024.jpg%20677w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22489%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESwati%20Narayan%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EUNEQUAL%3A%20Why%20India%20Lags%20Behind%20Its%20Neighbours%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EWestland%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20even%20more%20shocked%20when%20I%20walked%20up%20to%20a%20neighbouring%20house.%20Peeping%20through%20the%20window%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20severely%20disabled%20boy%20huddled%20inside%20a%20dark%20room.%20I%20was%20heartbroken%20to%20find%20that%20he%20had%20been%20kept%20hidden%20away%20like%20this.%20His%20mother%2C%20with%20teary%20eyes%2C%20asked%20us%20if%20we%20could%20help%20in%20any%20way.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20had%20to%20tell%20her%20that%20neither%20of%20us%20were%20medical%20practitioners%20but%20that%20we%20would%20love%20to%20speak%20to%20her%20son.%20When%20Bhim%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20courtyard%2C%20he%20flashed%20an%20unforgettable%20smile.%20I%20impressed%20upon%20his%20mother%20that%2C%20ideally%2C%20he%20should%20be%20exposed%20to%20some%20sunlight%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhim%E2%80%99s%20unspeakably%20poor%20parents%20were%20at%20their%20wit%E2%80%99s%20end.%20There%20was%20no%20healthcare%20facility%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20They%20loved%20their%20son%2C%20but%20simply%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20for%20him.%20I%20felt%20just%20as%20helpless.%20On%20the%20spur%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20stand%20together%20for%20family%20photo.%20Later%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20print%20the%20grainy%20image%20along%20with%20a%20disability%20pension%20form%20to%20hand%20over%20to%20Bhim%E2%80%99s%20mother.%20But%20I%20knew%20fully%20well%20that%2C%20at%20best%2C%20these%20were%20only%20symbolic%20gestures%20of%20comfort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20just%20one%20home.%20During%20our%20survey%20in%20Bihar%2C%20we%20met%20many%20families%20in%20similar%20or%20even%20worse%20predicaments%2C%20struggling%20with%20chronic%20ailments.%20They%20wage%20a%20daily%20battle%20against%20the%20criminal%20neglect%20of%20public%20healthcare%20in%20India.%20The%20poorest%20families%20pay%20the%20indescribably%20heaviest%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reach%20this%20distant%20village%2C%20we%20had%20crossed%20a%20river%20on%20a%20precarious%20boat%20that%20two%20men%20somehow%20rowed%20using%20only%20bamboo%20poles.%20The%20narrow%20deck%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Edinghy%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20been%20packed%20with%20fifteen-odd%20bicycles%20and%20a%20few%20motorcycles%20(including%20our%20own).%20A%20bevy%20of%20weary%20villagers%20with%20their%20jute%20sacks%2C%20chickens%20and%20household%20wares%20had%20jostled%20for%20space.%20It%20was%20a%20miracle%20we%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20toppled%20over.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20monsoon%2C%20such%20rickety%20boats%20were%20the%20primary%20means%20of%20transport%20across%20the%20flooded%20plains%20of%20Bihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETravelling%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%20of%20Nepal%20was%20equally%20tricky.%20One%20of%20the%20randomly%20selected%20villages%20for%20my%20survey%20was%20said%20to%20be%20three%20hours%20away%20from%20the%20district%20headquarters.%20But%20the%20journey%20ultimately%20took%20seven%20hours.%20After%20two%20hours%20on%20the%20rickety%20bus%2C%20we%20came%20across%20the%20raging%20Kamlamai%20river%2C%20which%20had%20flooded%20due%20to%20the%20rains.%20The%20veteran%20driver%20calmly%20stopped%20the%20bus%20midstream.%20Two%20conductors%20stepped%20out%20and%2C%20walking%20with%20meditative%20steps%20in%20the%20rushing%20current%2C%20surveyed%20the%20riverbed.%20After%20three%20hours%20of%20these%20rudimentary%20explorations%2C%20the%20driver%20finally%20figured%20out%20the%20best%20route%20to%20navigate%20the%20bus%20across%20the%20river.%20As%20passengers%20stuck%20inside%2C%20we%20had%20our%20stomachs%20in%20knots.%20Finally%2C%20when%20the%20bus%20reached%20the%20shore%2C%20all%20of%20us%20broke%20into%20a%20spontaneous%20round%20of%20claps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20perilous%20terrain%2C%20this%20far-removed%20Nepali%20village%20had%20relatively%20good%20healthcare%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20Bihar%20next%20door.%20When%20I%20suffered%20a%20sudden%20bout%20of%20severe%20vertigo%2C%20my%20Nepali%20translator%20Bijeta%20literally%20saved%20my%20life.%20The%20private%20pharmacy%20she%20took%20me%20to%20was%20a%20blessing%2C%20even%20with%20its%20limited%20stock%20of%20medicines.%20The%20shop%20even%20had%20beds%20in%20a%20room%20at%20the%20back%20to%20administer%20saline%20drips%20to%20patients.%20Later%2C%20when%20we%20finally%20reached%20the%20well-stocked%20government%20clinic%20an%20hour%20away%2C%20we%20met%20the%20health%20worker%20Gopal.%20Though%20he%20was%20not%20a%20doctor%2C%20he%20had%2017%20years%20of%20experience%20under%20his%20belt.%20Gopal%20used%20his%20stethoscope%20and%20blood%20pressure%20instrument%20to%20check%20my%20extremely%20low%20BP.%20Both%20his%20medical%20skills%20and%20endearing%20pidgin%20English%20lifted%20our%20spirits%20instantly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20health%20posts%20in%20Nepal%20are%20also%20managed%20by%20junior%20doctors.%20Unlike%20India%2C%20the%20Nepali%20government%20insists%20that%20all%20private%20medical%20colleges%20offer%20some%20students%20free%20education%20with%20full%20scholarship.%20After%20completion%20of%20their%20degrees%2C%20these%20young%20doctors%20have%20to%20serve%20in%20rural%20areas%20as%20a%20part%20of%20their%20two-year%20mandatory%20government%20service%20bond.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%C2%A0Unequal%3A%20Why%20India%20Lags%20Behind%20Its%20Neighbours%2C%C2%A0Swati%20Narayan%2C%20Westland%20Books%2C%20Context%20Imprint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESwati%20Narayan%20is%20an%20academic%20and%20activist.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Public%20Health%20and%20Human%20Development%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701934252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07112307%2Ffd42a93e-1b05-4602-adbc-827125ca5f01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fexcerpt-why-indias-social-development-indicators-lag-behind-its-neighbours%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Swati%20Narayan's%20'UNEQUAL'%20offers%20a%20comparison%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20social%20development%20indicators%20with%20that%20of%20its%20South%20Asian%20neighbours%20and%20an%20immersive%20examination%20of%20why%20India%20lags%20behind%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fexcerpt-why-indias-social-development-indicators-lag-behind-its-neighbours%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Years%20On%2C%20Union%20Asks%20for%20Another%20Week%E2%80%99s%20Time%20to%20Submit%20Guidelines%20for%20Seizure%20of%20Devices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20on%20Wednesday%20(December%206)%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20guidelines%20to%20regulate%20the%20seizure%20of%20phones%20and%20other%20digital%20devices%20of%20media%20professionals%20and%20individuals%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Eready%20by%20next%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20seeking%20framing%20of%20guidelines%20on%20the%20matter%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20did%20we%20issue%20notice%3F%20Some%20time%20frame%20has%20to%20be%20followed.%20Two%20years%20have%20passed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20(ASG)%20S.V.%20Raju%20informed%20them%20that%20a%20committee%20had%20been%20formed%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20would%20require%20more%20time%20to%20formulate%20the%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20ASG%20Raju%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20the%20guidelines%20would%20be%20ready%20by%20next%20week%2C%20the%20bench%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CGet%20it%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20on%20December%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20nearly%20300%20journalists%20were%20raided%20in%20the%20recent%20case%20involving%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Nitya%20Ramakrishnan%20argued%20for%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20these%20guidelines.%20She%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Ecopies%20of%20necessary%20data%20on%20devices%20could%20be%20taken%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20seizing%20the%20entire%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Circulates%20Interim%20Guidelines%20for%20Seizure%20of%20Devices%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%20of%20the%20matter%20on%20November%207%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20that%20search%20and%20seizure%20of%20media%20professionals%E2%80%99%20devices%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20matter%E2%80%9D%20as%20it%20involved%20confidential%20sources%20and%20their%20right%20to%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20media%20professionals%2C%20they%20will%20have%20on%20their%20phone%E2%80%99s%20sources%2C%20contacts.%20So%2C%20there%20must%20be%20some%20guidelines.%20This%20is%20serious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASG%20Raju%20had%20countered%20this%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20media%20cannot%20be%20above%20the%20law%20and%20there%20may%20be%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20elements%20so%20the%20government%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20%E2%80%9Cshut%20out%20completely%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbalancing%20of%20interests%E2%80%9D%20including%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fnews%2Fguidelines-on-search-or-seizure-of-digital-devices-of-media-professionals-to-be-prepared-soon-centre-tells-sc%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20to%20be%20a%20balancing%20of%20interests%20and%20better%20guidelines%20need%20to%20be%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20media%20professionals.%20We%20would%20like%20ASG%20to%20work%20on%20this%20and%20come%20back%20on%20this%20issue.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20aspect%20that%20privacy%20is%20held%20to%20be%20a%20fundamental%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20had%20said%20in%20its%20order%20on%20November%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20the%20last%20hearing%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20had%20circulated%20interim%20guidelines%20for%20seizure%20of%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20by%20five%20renowned%20academics%20%E2%80%93%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Madhava%20Prasad%2C%20Sujata%20Patel%2C%20Deepak%20Malghan%20and%20Mukul%20Kesavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20into%20account%20the%20circulated%20draft%20of%20guidelines%20and%20submit%20a%20response%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701932282000%2C%22visual%22%3A