-ias-topper-tips-essay-paper-cse-mains-interview-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessay%20writing%20%3C%2Fa%3Edoes%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20strategy%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wondered%20what%20kind%20of%20writing%20engages%20me%20as%20a%20reader.%20I%20would%20read%20the%20editorial%20section%20of%20The%20Hindu%20and%20write%20down%20my%20inference%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20story.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20incorporated%20that%20same%20style%20in%20my%20answer%20writing.%20Your%20essay%20should%20be%20crisp%2C%20engaging%2C%20and%20backed%20by%20facts.%20You%20can%20also%20include%20flowcharts%20to%20make%20answers%20interesting%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20fancy%20answers%20in%20the%20interview%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333542%2Fupsc-cse-interview-round-tips-by-ias-officers-personality-test-toppers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20IAS%20officer%20%3C%2Fa%3Esays%20she%20did%20not%20give%20any%20fancy%20answers%20to%20the%20interviewers.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%20myself%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20an%20instance%20from%20her%20interview.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20state-level%20silver%20medalist%20in%20taekwondo.%20I%20remember%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20looked%20so%20fragile%20and%20that%20it%20did%20not%20look%20like%20I%20could%20practice%20taekwondo.%20I%20politely%20said%20that%20strength%20matters%20more%20than%20physical%20appearance.%20I%20was%20not%20like%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20my%20god%2C%20sir%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20willpower%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20too%20senior%3B%20they%20understand%20when%20you%20are%20not%20being%20yourself.%20They%20do%20not%20appreciate%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Saloni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C