s%20ensures%20that%20if%20the%20surgeon%20looks%20away%20from%20the%20monitor%2C%20even%20while%20moving%20their%20hands%2C%20the%20system%20will%20not%20respond.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20safety%20measure%20that%20requires%20the%20camera%20view%20to%20be%20within%20sight%20for%20operation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20also%20has%20a%2023-inch%20large%20monitor%20with%20all%20controls%20easily%20accessible%20to%20the%20surgeon.%20This%20allows%20the%20surgeon%20to%20retrieve%20any%20of%20the%20DICOM%20images%20from%20the%20server%2C%20whether%20in%20the%20radiology%20department%20or%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20display%20them%20conveniently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20team%20has%20developed%20proprietary%20technology%20that%20enables%20them%20to%20convert%20these%20images%20into%203D%20models.%20Following%20this%2C%20a%20surgeon%20or%20a%20trainee%20can%20manipulate%20and%20slice%20through%20the%20images%2C%20essentially%20having%20the%20entire%20anatomy%20of%20the%20region%20you%E2%80%99re%20operating%20on%20right%20in%20front%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20not%20only%20makes%20the%20procedure%20safer%20and%20faster%20but%20also%20simplifies%20it%20by%20eliminating%20guesswork%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sudhir%20once%20sold%20his%20car%20and%20furniture%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20for%20the%20robot.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2